<!-- ============================================================================
     SECTION 9 — Configurator (Build Your Everest · live SKU builder)
     -------------------------------------------------------------------------
     SKU PATTERN (per LFLD Everest datasheet pg 3 ordering guide):
       LFLD-{wattage}-{cct}/{series}/{voltage}/{finish}{mount}/{optic}/{taa}

       Element decode:
         LFLD                   LED Sports Lighter family code
         {wattage}              480 / 600 / 850 / 1200 (5 catalog entries)
         -{cct}                 -57 (5700K · R1) · -40 / -50 (4000K / 5000K · R2) · -RGB (R3)
         /{series}              /R1 (Everest-I) · /R2 (Everest-II) · /R3 (Everest-III)
         /{voltage}             /U universal 120-277V (QS) · /H 120-277V high-voltage (MTO)
         /{finish}{mount}       /B/TR · Black + Trunnion (only QS combo)
         /{optic}               /O30 (default) · /O20 (narrow beam swap)
         /{taa}                 blank (Standard non-TAA) · /TAA (Mexico-made MTO)

     The 5 catalog wattage entries (per ordering guide, pg 3):
       1. 480W  · R3 · U or HV · QS · RGB only
       2. 600W  · R2 · U or HV · QS · 4000K or 5000K · WATTSELECT 300/450/600
       3. 150W  · R1 · U or HV · QS · 5700K only
       4. 1200W · R1 · H 120-277V · MTO · 5700K (HV variant)
       5. 1200W · R2 · U or HV · QS · 4000K or 5000K · WATTSELECT 800/1000/1200

     Cross-field constraints enforced by the JS engine:
       · Series picks drive Wattage + CCT availability
       · R1 1200W requires H voltage and stamps the SKU as MTO
       · R3 480W is RGB-only (CCT chip locks to RGB)
       · R2 600W and R2 1200W support both 4000K and 5000K + both U and H

     User-pickable fields:
       Required SKU Fields (LEFT column):
         1. Series                 R1 ★ (default · 150W traditional) · R2 · R3
         2. Wattage                varies per series
         3. CCT                    varies per series (R3 RGB locked)
         4. Voltage                U ★ (QS) · H (MTO · 120-277V)
         5. Finish + Mount         B/TR (locked · only QS combo per datasheet)
       Optional SKU Add-ons (RIGHT column):
         6. Optic                  O30 ★ (default · 30°) · O20 (20° swap)
         7. TAA Compliance         Standard ★ · TAA-Compliant (MTO Mexico variant)

     Default complete SKU: LFLD-850-57/R1/U/B/TR/O30 (R1 traditional · 5700K · U · O30)

     CFG-ZOHO-1: catalog match indicator surfaces "Catalog SKU" vs "Custom build"
     based on the 4 active catalog SKUs from the datasheet ordering guide:
       LFLD-850-57/R1/U/B/TR/O30
       LFLD-600-50/R2/U/B/TR/O30
       LFLD-1200-50/R2/U/B/TR/O30 (the bid-sheet flagship)
       LFLD-480-RGB/R3/U/B/TR/O30

     Submittal CTA opens submittal_template.html?product=everest&sku=…
     Submittal template carries EVEREST CFG block (handled in next pass).
     ============================================================================ -->
